{"tid":251551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[潔淨撚]刷牙用幾多牙膏?","createTime":"2017-05-21T04:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T06:46:38.000Z","uid":94315,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65796351b855ec324e87f7447f7f1cce1f698dd9","tid":251551,"uid":94315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"老母成日話我用牙膏用好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話牙醫建議系一粒豆既份量就夠，不過我鐘意成口泡，咁先刷得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.deardoctor.com/images/ddwc/features/managing-tooth-decay-chronic-diseases/correct-amount-of-toothpaste.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.deardoctor.com%2Fimages%2Fddwc%2Ffeatures%2Fmanaging-tooth-decay-chronic-diseases%2Fcorrect-amount-of-toothpaste.jpg&h=a6998438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家平時用幾多?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟牙醫建議一粒豆大小<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔刷牙架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n其他分量既請講低"},{"pid":"9e9af752588b176b9be17fb9b7ca261028ea5add","tid":251551,"uid":1436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"次次唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多咪刷耐啲<br />\n少咪刷兩下就算"},{"pid":"99dc47736eeb130b7d2ed14a0bd2bbb6af6cb2f9","tid":251551,"uid":94315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多咪刷耐啲<br />\n少咪刷兩下就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刷2下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴定絲?"},{"pid":"770affdcdac206a65167107291dbf01088cd987c","tid":251551,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike"